<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="act-on">act on</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-act-upon">1.★ <strong>按照...行事(act upon)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Why didn’t you act on her suggestion? 
你为什么不按照她的建议来做呢？</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>对... 起作用 / 有影响：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Alcohol acts quickly on the brain. 
酒精对大脑迅速产生影响。</p></div></div>